302.title: Punishment for Murder
302.description: Whoever commits murder shall be punished with death, or imprisonment for life.

376.title: Punishment for Rape
376.description: Whoever commits rape shall be punished with rigorous imprisonment for a term not less than ten years, which may extend to imprisonment for life.

498A.title: Husband or Relative of Husband of a Woman Subjecting Her to Cruelty
498A.description: Whoever, being the husband or the relative of the husband of a woman, subjects her to cruelty shall be punished with imprisonment for a term which may extend to three years and shall also be liable to fine.

420.title: Cheating and Dishonestly Inducing Delivery of Property
420.description: Whoever cheats and dishonestly induces another person to deliver any property shall be punished with imprisonment which may extend to seven years and shall also be liable to fine.

307.title: Attempt to Murder
307.description: Whoever does any act with such intention or knowledge, and under such circumstances that, if he by that act caused death, he would be guilty of murder, shall be punished with imprisonment which may extend to ten years, and shall also be liable to fine.

323.title: Punishment for Voluntarily Causing Hurt
323.description: Whoever, except in the case provided for by Section 334, voluntarily causes hurt shall be punished with imprisonment which may extend to one year, or with fine, or with both.

324.title: Voluntarily Causing Hurt by Dangerous Weapons or Means
324.description: Whoever voluntarily causes hurt by dangerous weapons or means shall be punished with imprisonment which may extend to three years, or with fine, or with both.

354.title: Assault or Criminal Force to Woman with Intent to Outrage Her Modesty
354.description: Whoever assaults or uses criminal force to any woman, intending to outrage or knowing it to be likely that he will thereby outrage her modesty, shall be punished with imprisonment which may extend to two years, or with fine, or with both.

363.title: Punishment for Kidnapping
363.description: Whoever kidnaps shall be punished with imprisonment which may extend to seven years, and shall also be liable to fine.

366.title: Kidnapping, Abducting or Inducing Woman to Compel Her Marriage, etc.
366.description: Whoever kidnaps or abducts any woman with intent that she may be compelled to marry any person against her will or forced or seduced to illicit intercourse shall be punished with imprisonment which may extend to ten years, and shall also be liable to fine.
